- have a nodejs app like below
- let it run and see how uuids are printed
- take a heap snapshot after ~1min
- let it runs for another while (~2min)
- take another heap snapshot, heap grew by a few MB

```
var uuid = require('node-uuid');

console.log('starting');
setInterval(() => console.log(uuid.v4()), 100);

```
